text: Karat-Tamak () is a rural locality (a village) in Starotuymazinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 78 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Tuymazy, 4 km from Staryye Tuymazy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Karat-Tamak
